OL,3,CProgramme listings for WED 15 APR
OL,4,G2115FMy Week With Guerrilla Girls
OL,5,     GKate Bryan explores the lives of
OL,6,     Gthe Guerrilla Girls, a group of
OL,7,     Gart activists who haven't granted
OL,8,     Ga film crew full access to their
OL,9,     Glives and work in over 30 years.
OL,10,G2215FWelcome to the Eighties
OL,11,     GAmid 80s glam, gothic artists
OL,12,     Greject materialism, delving into
OL,13,     Gexistence, transience, decay and
OL,14,     Gdisillusionment over
OL,15,     Gsuperficiality.
OL,16,G2330FMadness: Live At House Of Common
OL,17,     GSka legends Madness headline the
OL,18,     GAugust 2016 House of Common
OL,19,     Gfestival at Clapham Common,
OL,20,     GLondon, with a set featuring Our
OL,21,     GHouse and It Must Be Love.
