OL,5,     GMelencolia I, by Albrecht Durer:
OL,6,     GCreated in 1514 and widely
OL,7,     Gregarded as the greatest print
OL,8,     Gever made, Durer's Melencolia has
OL,9,     Gdefied all attempts to understand
OL,10,     Git.
OL,11,G0530FThe Art Mysteries
OL,12,     GFountain by Marcel Duchamp: Voted
OL,13,     Gthe most influential artwork of
OL,14,     Gthe 20th century, Marcel
OL,15,     GDuchamp's upturned urinal changed
OL,16,     Gthe course of art - creating
OL,17,     G'conceptual art'.
